|author= Carter, Bill
|url= http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0CE0DD143FF933A05752C0A964958260
|title=  'L.A. Law,' to Halt Slide, Reaches Back to Bochco
|publisher= [[紐約時報|紐約時報]]
|accessdate=2008-03-26}}</ref> 
